  "body": "## Overview\r\n\r\nThis pull request introduces a complete documentation suite for BlockScope, covering both user-facing and developer-facing materials.\r\n\r\nThe goal is to formalize onboarding, usage guidance, contribution standards, and review processes for the project.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Documentation Added\r\n\r\n### User Documentation\r\n- `USER_GUIDE.md` ΓÇô Setup and usage guide (Docker + local development)\r\n- `FAQ.md` ΓÇô 15+ frequently asked questions\r\n- `EXAMPLES.md` ΓÇô Real API usage examples with accurate responses\r\n- `VIDEO_TUTORIAL_SCRIPT.md` ΓÇô Docker + React walkthrough script\r\n\r\n### Developer Onboarding\r\n- `CONTRIBUTING.md` ΓÇô Contribution guidelines and workflow\r\n- `CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md` ΓÇô Contributor behavior standards\r\n- `CODE_REVIEW_CHECKLIST.md` ΓÇô Professional review checklist\r\n- `DEV_SETUP_VIDEO_SCRIPT.md` ΓÇô Developer environment setup walkthrough\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Key Improvements\r\n\r\n- Standardized PR workflow documentation\r\n- Defined branching and commit conventions\r\n- Formalized review criteria\r\n- Documented Docker and local development setup\r\n- Provided accurate API examples based on current implementation\r\n- Added security considerations for contributors\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Scope\r\n\r\nThis PR:\r\n- Adds documentation files only\r\n- Does not modify application logic\r\n- Does not alter backend, frontend, or infrastructure code\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\n- Documentation reviewed for consistency with current API behavior\r\n- Examples reflect actual scan responses\r\n- Severity keys match current implementation (`critical`, `high`, etc.)\r\n- No hardcoded secrets included\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Outcome\r\n\r\nBlockScope now has structured, production-quality documentation comparable to professional open-source projects.\r\n\r\nReady for review.",
